AUDIENCE: Don't always
do marketing for you.

00:47:30.320 --> 00:47:33.010
Apparently they only do that for
you if you are already famous

00:47:33.010 --> 00:47:35.260
or if they have some reason
to think that your book is

00:47:35.260 --> 00:47:36.224
going to be famous.

00:47:36.224 --> 00:47:37.640
But my friend who's
been published

00:47:37.640 --> 00:47:40.349
by Random Penguin and some
other famous publisher--

00:47:40.349 --> 00:47:42.140
ALON HALEVY: It's Random
House and Penguin.

