AUDIENCE: Well,
they've joined forces,

00:47:43.540 --> 00:47:44.530
so now they're Random Penguin.

00:47:44.530 --> 00:47:45.680
ALON HALEVY: OK,
Random [INAUDIBLE].

00:47:45.680 --> 00:47:46.435
AUDIENCE: Well,
I don't know what

00:47:46.435 --> 00:47:47.559
